      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=sd0pcjy64y]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=sd0pcjy64y]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=n9gj2x4ztj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=n9gj2x4ztj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=a4xyqedhze]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=a4xyqedhze]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=e98z251zbu]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=e98z251zbu]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"a4xyqedhze\">Resource</span></strong>: IES Profiles</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"sd0pcjy64y\">Library Created By</span></strong>: Dylan Sisson</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"e98z251zbu\">Updated by</span></strong>: Leif Pedersen</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"n9gj2x4ztj\">Use</span></strong>: Attach to RenderMan lights</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/ies_profiles/9035_ies_profiles_v21.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608403471\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"1f8f224b-d188-4694-87d7-2ae9aa2610a9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473791&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"IESProfiles-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>This is a library of production-ready lights for RenderMan, featuring 19 IES profiles.</p><p>IES profiles help you achieve physical photometric data distribution, in other words, a realistic light emission pattern based on original manufacturer specifications, giving your art an extra dose of realism.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d3ad4cde-ea6a-4bbb-89cc-2fb5d2c073b3\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>For more information about IES profiles, see <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.cgarena.com/freestuff/tutorials/max/ieslights/\" rel=\"nofollow\">CGArena</a>.</p></div></div><p>This library of IES lights includes the following IES profiles ...</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283661606&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=643\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283661606&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"719\" data-width=\"849\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607912291\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3141727d-046e-4268-bf4d-371aaaf11c00\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283661606&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=1286 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9034_screen_shot_2017_01_23_at_104247_am.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283661606&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=643 1x\" /></span><h2 id=\"IESProfiles-How-to\">How-to</h2><p>To install in RenderMan's Preset Browser, place the <strong>IES</strong> folder inside your RenderMan Asset Library's <strong>LightRigs</strong> folder. It is recommended that you transfer the installation default RenderManAssetLibrary folder to a non-install location with full writing privileges.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283684843&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=336\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283684843&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"728\" data-width=\"1644\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607846679\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"84952dde-b059-4e7a-99b6-29ab65f39571\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283684843&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=672 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/9032_ies_folder_structure.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283684843&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=336 1x\" /></span><p>Once you transfer the Materials folder and move your Asset Library into a different location, it is essential to tell Maya through the preferences that you want to use the new path.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758283701580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758283701580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"622\" data-width=\"776\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608403480\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3d5d3347-bcf9-42aa-bff9-52b1d0f0594f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758283701580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=776&amp;height=622 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1758283701580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609 1x\" /></span><p>Or you can create a new environment variable in your Maya.env file like so:</p><p><code>RMAN_ASSET_LIBRARY = /My/Folder/Example/RenderManAssetLibrary</code></p><p>This will make sure you are always pointing to the correct folder.</p><hr /><h3 id=\"IESProfiles-Copyright\">Copyright</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Public Domain. Free of known copyright restrictions.</a></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"cc-zero.png\" width=\"127\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283475528&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=127&amp;height=44\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283475528&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"142\" data-width=\"403\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608403477\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"cc-zero.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"949cb1db-0cd5-4d4d-bcbf-cce0334aa920\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283475528&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=254&amp;height=88 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283475528&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=127&amp;height=44 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608403457/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608403468\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608403457\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"0dc1877e-d115-417a-a30a-42450a06b46b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608403457/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758283473790&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
